{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-header",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Agora v1.2 — Multi-Agent LLM Debate\n",
    "\n",
    "Four frontier models debate a topic in structured rounds, guided by an independent judge, until they produce an executive synthesis.\n",
    "\n",
    "| Role | Model |\n",
    "|---|---|\n",
    "| Analyst A | GPT-4.1 (Azure OpenAI) |\n",
    "| Analyst B | Gemini 2.5 Pro (Google) |\n",
    "| Analyst C | Claude Opus 4.7 (Anthropic) |\n",
    "| Analyst D | Grok-3 — The Disruptor (xAI) |\n",
    "| Judge | Grok-3 (xAI) |\n",
    "\n",
    "**To run a new debate:** edit `tema.txt` and `marco.txt`, then Run All."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-imports",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys\n",
    "\n",
    "# Reload modules on every run so edits to debate.py / prompts.py take effect immediately\n",
    "for mod in [\"debate\", \"prompts\"]:\n",
    "    sys.modules.pop(mod, None)\n",
    "\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, r\"D:\\Dropbox\\Personal\\Documentos\\Personal\\Proyectos\\Agora\\v1.2\")\n",
    "from debate import run_debate\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Ready.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-config",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "\n",
    "_base = Path(r\"D:\\Dropbox\\Personal\\Documentos\\Personal\\Proyectos\\Agora\\v1.2\")\n",
    "\n",
    "TOPIC     = (_base / \"tema.txt\").read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\").strip()\n",
    "FRAMEWORK = (_base / \"marco.txt\").read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\").strip()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"TOPIC     ({len(TOPIC)} chars): {TOPIC[:120]}{'...' if len(TOPIC) > 120 else ''}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\nFRAMEWORK ({len(FRAMEWORK)} chars): {FRAMEWORK[:120]}{'...' if len(FRAMEWORK) > 120 else ''}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-run",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "run_debate(TOPIC, FRAMEWORK)"
   ]
  }
 ],
